title: Cleaning the Filters: Dirt Devil Quick Power Upright UD70115
transcripts: Two removing clean the filters put the cleaner in the upright position turn the power off and unplug the power cord remove the dirt cup and set it aside. Press in firmly to remove the filter cover and take out the filter cartridge for quick filter cleaning. Tap the pleated filter on the inside of the trash can. You can brush off the foam filter reassemble the filter cartridge and put it back into the cleaner. It is important to clean the filter after every use and replace the filter every six months depending on use for more thorough cleaning. You can rinse the foam filter and the plated cartridge with tap water. Do not use soap or detergent dry for at least 24 hours before reassembling the filter cartridge and putting it back into the cleaner. Visit our website to buy filters on line or call our toll free customer service number.
